com.test.automation.framework.pagemodel

Class Browser

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.test.automation.framework.pagemodel.Browser

  • public class Browser
extends java.lang.Object
    Utility to provide Page Object Model support in the framework. This class provides all the utilities to create and navigate between page objects.
    Author:
    Varun Menon

      • to

        public <T> T to(java.lang.Class<? extends PageClass> pageClass)
        Navigates to said page after appending the base url to Page url. This utility also verifies whether the driver is at the said Page by using "at" method of the Page after navigation.
        Parameters:
        pageClass - - Page class extending PageClass to where the driver have to be navigated.
        Returns:
        The said page class object once verification is successful.

      • to

        public <T> T to(java.lang.Class<? extends PageClass> pageClass,
       java.io.File file)
        Navigates to said page after appending the base url to Page url and initializes any PageFactory based WebElements in the said class using the provided locator file. This utility also verifies whether the driver is at the said Page by using "at" method of the Page after navigation.
        Parameters:
        pageClass - - Page class extending PageClass to where the driver have to be navigated.
        file - - File object of the file containing the key/value pair of the locators.
        Returns:
        The said page class object once verification is successful.

      • isAt

      • getPageObject

        public <T> T getPageObject(java.lang.Class<? extends PageClass> pageClass)
        Utility to create and get the said page class object. This utility directly creates the said page class object and returns it. No navigation or verification is done for the said page.
        Parameters:
        pageClass - Page class extending PageClass for which the object has to be created and returned.
        Returns:
        The said page class object

      • getPageObject

        public <T> T getPageObject(java.lang.Class<? extends PageClass> pageClass,
                  java.io.File file)
        Utility to create and get the said page class object. This utility directly creates the said page class object and returns it. No navigation or verification is done for the said page.

        This method initializes any PageFactory based WebElements present in the said class using the provided locator file.

        Parameters:
        pageClass - Page class extending PageClass for which the object has to be created and returned.
        file - - File object of the file containing the key/value pair of the locators.
        Returns:
        The said page class object
